  <entry>
    <title>谷歌云机器运维</title>
    <url>/2021/03/05/Google-Hey/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h3 id="0x01-前言"><a href="#0x01-前言" class="headerlink" title="0x01  前言"></a>0x01  前言</h3><p>每次白嫖谷歌云，都要重新部署服务器，此篇记录一下，日后好翻看。服务器是debain10。</p>
<span id="more"></span>

<h3 id="0x02-ssh免密登录"><a href="#0x02-ssh免密登录" class="headerlink" title="0x02  ssh免密登录"></a>0x02  ssh免密登录</h3><figure class="highlight txt"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">//在windows的用户目录下创建.ssh文件夹</span><br><span class="line">mkdir ~/.ssh</span><br><span class="line">cd .ssh</span><br><span class="line">ssh-keygen -t rsa -C &quot;xxxx@qq.com&quot;,后面接3个回车</span><br><span class="line">//登录linux服务器</span><br><span class="line">mkdir ~/.ssh</span><br><span class="line">vi ~/.ssh/authorized_keys</span><br><span class="line">//.ssh目录下生成的id_rsa.pub文件发送到linux根目录</span><br><span class="line">cat ~/id_rsa.pub &gt;&gt; ~/.ssh/authorized_keys</span><br><span class="line">//删除服务器的id_rsa.pub</span><br><span class="line">rm ~/id_rsa.pub</span><br><span class="line">//重启ssh服务</span><br><span class="line">service sshd restart</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="0x03-配置ssh会话永不过期"><a href="#0x03-配置ssh会话永不过期" class="headerlink" title="0x03  配置ssh会话永不过期"></a>0x03  配置ssh会话永不过期</h3><figure class="highlight txt"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">vi /etc/ssh/sshd_config</span><br><span class="line">ClientAliveInterval 60</span><br><span class="line">ClientAliveCountMax 3</span><br><span class="line">service sshd restart</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="0x04-screen"><a href="#0x04-screen" class="headerlink" title="0x04  screen"></a>0x04  screen</h3><p>screen，这是一款ssh会话管理工具</p>
<figure class="highlight txt"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">//安装screen</span><br><span class="line">apt-get install screen</span><br><span class="line">//使用screen</span><br><span class="line">screen -S test          //创建一个名为test的session</span><br><span class="line">screen -ls              //列出当前所有的session</span><br><span class="line">screen -r test          //回到test的session</span><br><span class="line">screen -S test -X quit  //删除会话</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="0x05-安装谷歌浏览器"><a href="#0x05-安装谷歌浏览器" class="headerlink" title="0x05  安装谷歌浏览器"></a>0x05  安装谷歌浏览器</h3><p>安装wegt</p>
<figure class="highlight txt"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">apt-get install wget</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>使用wegt下载最新的Google Chrome .deb程序包</p>
<figure class="highlight txt"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">wget https://dl.google.com/linux/direct/google-chrome-stable_current_amd64.deb</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>安装 Google Chrome</p>
<figure class="highlight txt"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">apt install ./google-chrome-stable_current_amd64.deb</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="0x06-Crawlergo-xray联动"><a href="#0x06-Crawlergo-xray联动" class="headerlink" title="0x06 Crawlergo+xray联动"></a>0x06 Crawlergo+xray联动</h3><p>下载<a href="https://github.com/chaitin/xray/releases/tag/1.7.0">xray</a></p>
<p>xray前期的配置</p>
<figure class="highlight txt"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">chmod +x xray_linux_amd64   </span><br><span class="line">./xray_linux_amd64 version  //查看版本</span><br><span class="line">./xray_linux_amd64 genca    //生成证书</span><br><span class="line">cp ca.crt /usr/local/share/ca-certificates/xray.crt //安装证书</span><br><span class="line">update-ca-certificates</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>下载<a href="https://github.com/timwhitez/crawlergo_x_XRAY">crawlergo+xray</a></p>
<p>配置好launcher.py的cmd变量中的crawlergo爬虫配置（主要是chrome路径转换本地路径）</p>
<figure class="highlight txt"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">/usr/bin/google-chrome</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>下载<a href="https://github.com/0Kee-Team/crawlergo">crawlergo</a></p>
<figure class="highlight txt"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">chmod +x crawlergo</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>开始扫描</p>
<figure class="highlight txt"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">第一步：xray启动被动扫描状态</span><br><span class="line">./xray_linux_amd64 webscan --listen 127.0.0.1:7777 --html-output 1.html</span><br><span class="line">第二步：python3运行launcher.py</span><br><span class="line">//debain系统默认安装了python3,但是没有安装pip，这里需要手动安装</span><br><span class="line">apt-get install python3-pip</span><br><span class="line">//安装库</span><br><span class="line">pip3 install simplejson</span><br><span class="line">pip3 install requests</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="0x07-安装python3-8"><a href="#0x07-安装python3-8" class="headerlink" title="0x07  安装python3.8"></a>0x07  安装python3.8</h3><figure class="highlight txt"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">//卸载python3.7</span><br><span class="line">apt-get remove python3.7</span><br><span class="line">//卸载python3.7及其依赖</span><br><span class="line">apt-get remove --auto-remove python3.7</span><br><span class="line">//清除python3.7</span><br><span class="line">sudo apt-get purge python3.7</span><br><span class="line">//安装python3.8</span><br><span class="line">//安装构建Python源所需的包</span><br><span class="line">apt update sudo apt install build-essential zlib1g-dev libsqlite3-dev libncurses5-dev libgdbm-dev libnss3-dev libssl-dev libreadline-dev libffi-dev wget</span><br><span class="line">//使用curl命令从Python下载页面下载最新版本的源代码</span><br><span class="line">curl -O https://www.python.org/ftp/python/3.8.3/Python-3.8.3.tgz</span><br><span class="line">//解压</span><br><span class="line">tar -xf Python-3.8.3.tgz</span><br><span class="line">//导航到Python源目录并运行configure脚本，该脚本将执行大量检查以确保系统上存在所有依赖项</span><br><span class="line">cd Python-3.8.3 ./configure --enable-optimizations</span><br><span class="line">//运行make以启动构建过程</span><br><span class="line">make -j 8</span><br><span class="line">//安装Python二进制文件</span><br><span class="line">make altinstall</span><br><span class="line">//修改python3.8为python3</span><br><span class="line">ln -s /usr/local/bin/python3.8 /usr/bin/python3</span><br><span class="line">//修改pip3.8为pip3</span><br><span class="line">ln -s /usr/local/bin/pip3.8 /usr/bin/pip3</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="0x08-安装oneforall"><a href="#0x08-安装oneforall" class="headerlink" title="0x08 安装oneforall"></a>0x08 安装oneforall</h3><figure class="highlight txt"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">//下载oneforall</span><br><span class="line">git clone https://gitee.com/shmilylty/OneForAll.git</span><br><span class="line">//安装</span><br><span class="line">python3 -m pip install -U pip setuptools wheel -i https://mirrors.aliyun.com/pypi/simple/</span><br><span class="line">pip3 install -r requirements.txt -i https://mirrors.aliyun.com/pypi/simple/</span><br><span class="line">python3 oneforall.py --help</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>







]]></content>
